Class ExchangeIds

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.opengamma.strata.product.common.ExchangeIds

  • public final class ExchangeIds
extends Object
    Identifiers for common exchanges.

    The identifier names are ISO Market Identifier Codes (MICs).
